channel.title: Cannot find objects
channel.description:
Hello,
I have just received the board and installed the software. I started by loading ready patches from the menu library/factory and library/community but library/home is empty. I figure out that this is why I cannot find anywhere the objects to build my patches. Where is the mistake ? Thank you very much for your help.

Home directory is usually empty.

The objects you find when you press the space bar in an empty window in edit mode (Not live mode)
